national-emergency-and-disaster.title: Surviving natural disaster
national-emergency-and-disaster.summary: If you have experience a national emergency or a disaster, help may be available, including temporary housing and financial help.
national-emergency-and-disaster.secondar: Government assistance after surviving natural disaster
national-emergency-and-disaster.eligibil: For the most accurate results, select the options that best describe your or the person applying for benefits situation. The list of benefits will reorder to prioritize the benefits you are most likely eligible for.
